ItemDesc: Broken teeth fragments left behind during the borisin conquests. Used to level up Traces slightly for <color=#f29e38ff>Destruction</color> characters.
ItemBGDesc: Borisin consider their teeth as a warrior's blade and weapon. The borisin worship warriors possessing supreme power. In their tribes, where the strong rule the weak, those with dental caries will only be discarded by the group. "O, Brood Lord, grant us sharp teeth and claws."
